  "detailed_description": "The canals of Venice, the Eiffel Tower, the… Bad Kebabs - ah, the joys of taking a trip through Europe. In Travelin’, you’ll be on a grand journey to discover both the best and worst of Europe, from intriguing countries like Iceland and Turkey to the perilous pitfalls of border controls and sketchy taxi drivers. Play your cards right, collect the most points, and double cross your fellow travelers to be crowned king of the road.<br><br>In Travelin’, your journey unfolds with every draw, offering you multiple possibilities to explore and master:<br><br>✈️ Collect tickets & visit countries to earn points.<br>🛑 Stop any potential negative impacts against you, ensuring that no one disrupts your strategy.<br>⚔️ Play an action card to create an advantage against your opponents.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486700/extras/ab89539a3ee1db5a3d40c306925a4a57.webp?t=1721408462\" width=600 height=48 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486700/extras/01f5b0f53350be5c220c81823275d6e0.poster.avif?t=1721408462\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486700/extras/01f5b0f53350be5c220c81823275d6e0.webm?t=1721408462\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486700/extras/01f5b0f53350be5c220c81823275d6e0.mp4?t=1721408462\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486700/extras/18539acd2e9657eae53d7411288a6208.webp?t=1721408462\" width=600 height=48 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486700/extras/b87489cb04c7ef868037434bf8e42127.poster.avif?t=1721408462\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486700/extras/b87489cb04c7ef868037434bf8e42127.webm?t=1721408462\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486700/extras/b87489cb04c7ef868037434bf8e42127.mp4?t=1721408462\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486700/extras/875484a31d5589e0bcc2b48ccdfc7286.webp?t=1721408462\" width=600 height=48 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486700/extras/974be7cf92047dd08206b5f04e59869a.poster.avif?t=1721408462\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486700/extras/974be7cf92047dd08206b5f04e59869a.webm?t=1721408462\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486700/extras/974be7cf92047dd08206b5f04e59869a.mp4?t=1721408462\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "The canals of Venice, the Eiffel Tower, the… Bad Kebabs - ah, the joys of taking a trip through Europe. In Travelin’, you’ll be on a grand journey to discover both the best and worst of Europe, from intriguing countries like Iceland and Turkey to the perilous pitfalls of border controls and sketchy taxi drivers. Play your cards right, collect the most points, and double cross your fellow travelers to be crowned king of the road.<br><br>In Travelin’, your journey unfolds with every draw, offering you multiple possibilities to explore and master:<br><br>✈️ Collect tickets & visit countries to earn points.<br>🛑 Stop any potential negative impacts against you, ensuring that no one disrupts your strategy.<br>⚔️ Play an action card to create an advantage against your opponents.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486700/extras/ab89539a3ee1db5a3d40c306925a4a57.webp?t=1721408462\" width=600 height=48 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486700/extras/01f5b0f53350be5c220c81823275d6e0.poster.avif?t=1721408462\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486700/extras/01f5b0f53350be5c220c81823275d6e0.webm?t=1721408462\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486700/extras/01f5b0f53350be5c220c81823275d6e0.mp4?t=1721408462\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486700/extras/18539acd2e9657eae53d7411288a6208.webp?t=1721408462\" width=600 height=48 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.st